reviewText: This is the fourth installment of the TV series Highway to Heaven.  Jonathan Smith and Mark Gordon travel from place to place helping those in need.  They reach out to show kindness and compassion are not a lost art  and that people are in great need of them.  This season brings notable guest stars like Bob Hope, Chad Allen and Bill Erwin.  This program is for people who like actors Michael Landon and Victor French and like spiritual content.
summary: Complete Season 4 of Highway to Heaven

reviewText: I have gotten dvds from Mill Creek before and have not minded that they stack the disks on top of each other as each disk tended to be also in a sleeve to protect the disk.  Well this time it was stacked on top of each other but NO SLEEVES to protect the disks.  That is a sure fire way to scratch the disks.  I immediately put them in a dvd holder that was setup to protect the disks.  Shame on you Mill Creek for being so cheap.
summary: glad this came out but the packaging stinks
